	<body>
		<p begin="00:00:00.50" end="00:00:03.70">Maria: Hi, Paolo! How are you?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:00.50" end="00:00:03.70">Maria: Hi, Paolo! How are you?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:03.70" end="00:00:05.63">Paolo: Fine, and you?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:05.63" end="00:00:07.47">Maria: Fine, thanks.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:07.47" end="00:00:09.32">Where are you going now? </p>
		<p begin="00:00:09.32" end="00:00:11.24">Paolo: I&apos;m going to work.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:11.24" end="00:00:14.52">Maria: Really? Where do you work?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:14.52" end="00:00:17.63">Paolo: I work in a restaurant.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:17.63" end="00:00:20.14">Maria: What is it called?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:20.14" end="00:00:23.36">Paolo: It&apos;s called Trattoria Margherita.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:23.36" end="00:00:26.03">It&apos;s on San Daniele Street.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:26.03" end="00:00:29.41">Maria: Do you work on the weekend, too?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:29.41" end="00:00:33.73">Paolo: Sometimes, but this Saturday I&apos;m going to the sea.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:33.73" end="00:00:35.33">Maria: How nice!</p>
		<p begin="00:00:35.33" end="00:00:36.77">Where are you going?</p>
		<p begin="00:00:36.77" end="00:00:39.44">Paolo: I&apos;m going to Ostia.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:39.44" end="00:00:42.57">Maria: My aunt lives in Ostia.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:42.57" end="00:00:44.68">It&apos;s a nice town.</p>
		<p begin="00:00:44.68" end="00:00:47.26">Paolo: Are you going away on Saturday?					</p>
		<p begin="00:00:47.26" end="00:00:53.11">Maria: No, I&apos;m going into town to buy a gift for a friend. </p>
